You can run xeoBabel
  1)  ./xeoBabel
  2)  java -jar xeoBabel.jar

you have to modify your profile (.bashrc or .profile or .cshrc, depending on the shell).
this is an example using the .bashrc

 3.)  export PATH="$PATH:this directoy" 


